description._content: Description: Dar-i-Khazinah, the sief, looking up-river with the water-pumping station to supply the Oil-Fields on the right of the picture. Location: Dar-i-Khazinah, Persia Description: Dar-i-Khazinah. Upper-river steamer arriving at the sief. Location: Dar-i-Khazinah, Persia Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/714 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives. Feel free to share it within the spirit of the Commons Please use the comments section below the pictures to share any information you have about the people, places or events shown.
